Preface
=======

This calculator helps design a simple T-section or Pi-network attenuator

T-Section
=========

The following diagram illustrates the key measurements.

..  image:: tatten.gif
    :alt: T-section Diagram

To compute resistors

1.  Enter network impedance in Ohms.

2.  Enter the attenuation in dB.

